'''BioFach''' is the world's largest [[trade fair]] for [[organic movement|organic]] [[organic food|food]] and [[organic agriculture|agriculture]]. It is held each year in the month of February, in [[Nuremberg]], [[Germany]]. It brings together 2774 exhibitors and approximately 46700 trade visitors from around 130 [[country|countries]].<ref name=Biofach>{{cite web|title=BioFach|url=http://www.biofach.de/en/|publisher=Biofach|accessdate=30 January 2013}}</ref> 

